        <https://w3id.org/narad_linkml/schema/narad/schema/:ElementKindEnum#RFCavity>,
        <https://w3id.org/narad_linkml/schema/narad/schema/:ElementKindEnum#Solenoid> .

<https://w3id.org/narad_linkml/schema/narad/schema/:DataTypeEnum> a owl:Class ;
